             sworn.</p>
               <p>I pursued the prisoner, and brought him back to Mr. Bell's, with the boots upon him.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I saw a boy go in and take the boots; I ran after him, and he dropped them; I picked them up, and this gentleman came and laid hold of me.</p>
